nodes.text: A clone served as a shock trooper with the Coruscant Guard around 21 BBY during the events of the Clone Wars.

Before the Separatists planned to bomb the Coruscant power generator, this clone shock trooper was on patrol at the docks under the derrick major. He was relieved when he saw the demolition droids, which were disguised as Sweeper Droids, arriving on the docks to clean and told them to get to work immediately.
This clone trooper was voiced by Dee Bradley Baker.
